      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, preserved in a state that rivals its original showroom debut. Every aspect of this vehicle\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, unblemished interior\u2014has been maintained to the highest possible standard. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality, offering both mechanical perfection and an aesthetic presence that is truly beyond reproach. For the discerning individual who accepts only the finest, this vehicle represents the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
