    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it looks and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new adventure, this is the one! Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
