    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) in concours-ready condition. This specimen features the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine, delivering 315hp through a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent borescope inspection confirming zero cylinder wall scoring. Performance is sharpened by a factory M030 sport suspension and a limited-slip differential. The Arctic Silver metallic paint retains its factory depth, while the interior shows negligible bolster wear. Fully serviced with a comprehensive binder of records, this 911 offers a visceral, analog driving experience with peerless throttle response and chassis rigidity.",
